       <p style="text-align:justify;padding:20px;"><font size="4pt" color="Black">Welcome to First Capital University of Bangladesh. FCUB was founded in 2012 under the private University Act. 1992 with a vision to create a global higher education center for excellence. As a developing country, we need to develop education sector to face the challenge of globalization. We specially ensure modern and career related education that has great demand in present job market in both Bangladesh and abroad. <br><br>To ensure quality education FCUB is equipped with modern infrastructural facilities, latest academic curricula, Internet with Wi-Fi facility, well ventilated classrooms, and seminar halls supported with multi-media, rich libraries, most sophisticated laboratories, students' cafeterias, standby generators, etc. <br><br>Today, FCUB continues to grow, both in its facilities and in the dimensions of its educational and research programs. The goals of FCUB include the continued provision of the highest quality education at the undergraduate and graduate levels along with increased support for outstanding research to meet the needs of society and to fulfill FCUBs role as a leading private university in Bangladesh.  </font></p>
